{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Lifetime driving ban if you are convicted of causing death by dangerous driving.",
        "additional_details": "My child was killed by a speeding driver,  Who was convicted of causing death by dangerous driving. My child suffered horrific instant death injuries, the driver was driving at speeds of 73-93mph when he hit her on a 30mph road, he was sentenced to 9 years minus 25% reduction for going guilty also given a 7 year driving ban to start immediately, when hes released he will have 4 years ban left. Driving is a luxury and it should be taken away if convicted of this crime. I've lost my child forever.",
        "background": "I would like to change the law on \"if you are  convicted for causing death by dangerous driving then a lifetime driving ban should be imposed\", they should never be allowed to drive again.",
